\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16258992 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3553086\charrsid12671005 You used to have these relations who came to stay, did your mother and father ever have friends visiting them, and neighbours?
