 the other, but otherwise, you know what I mean to say, it was just a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6447358\charrsid12671005 \{blank\} }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3553086\charrsid12671005 used to go out in those days, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16258992 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3553086\charrsid12671005 Did they ever give the 
neighbours, or did the neighbours give your mother and father anything in the way of entertainment, say, like tea or music, anything like that when they came round?
