\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3553086\charrsid12671005 s shop. I used to go on my rounds, you know, and deliver goods to them, but otherwise \'85 Well, there was that dividing line, we couldn't mistake it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16258992 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3553086\charrsid12671005 What about in church activities, did you come across middle class people, or their children, at all?
