\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2108855 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3553086\charrsid12671005 They were more or less like ourselves, Council workers, you know. At least, my father was.
