ll. I met real gentleman and I met real ladies. Now, if I tell you candidly, although those different classes existed in Hanwell, I'll say so today which I'd hate to say so often. There are no snobs in Hanwell, not in Hanwell as it is. There are no snobs.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16258992 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3553086\charrsid12671005 So these people that you'd call 'real ladies', they weren't snobbish?
